string.name: guide_remind_content_desc
string.value:
No more worries about missing the time because you're busy with other things.
No more troubles with forgetting what you wanted to do when you turn around.
Whatever you want to do, just note it down, and I'll remind you.

string.name: guide_target_content_desc
string.value:
Suddenly feeling anxious with no goals or plans?
Or perhaps you have goals and plans but always end up procrastinating?
Let XM record your goals and keep you on track with daily check-ins.

string.name: guide_memorandum_content_desc
string.value:
Life always has beautiful moments worth recording.
Whether it's words, emotions, or pictures, there are many ways to document life.
Occasionally looking back at them can be quite nice, too.
